          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>GI Bill Fairness Act of 2017</strong></p> <p>This bill includes as active duty, for purposes of eligibility for post-9/11 veterans educational assistance, service of a member of a reserve component ordered to active duty to receive authorized medical care, to be medically evaluated, or to complete a required Department of Defense health care study.</p>]]></text>
